HEADWORD: Epictetian
<hw>Ep`ic*te"tian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/, fr.
<?/ Epictetus.]</ety> <def>Pertaining to Epictetus, the Roman Stoic
philosopher, whose conception of life was to be passionless under
whatever circumstances.</def>⟦br⟧
